      "content": "okay i understand about the reye's thing but he's so out of it right now and it's making me really nervous. i dont have any calpol or nurofen here at the moment. isn't a small dose of aspirin usually fine for adults and wouldn't it work basically the same way for him? i just need the fever to break so he can sleep.",
